        <mxCell id="p7-d3-5" value="&lt;b&gt;5. Build YouTube → email → consult funnel&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Automated: watch → subscribe → get free PDF → book call&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font style='font-size:7px;' color='#1e8449'&gt;This is what turns YouTube into a $40K engine&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=9;fillColor=#eafaf1;strokeColor=#1e8449;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
